            <listBibl>
              <bibl>It is possible that this Commentator may be Claude de Saumaise [Salmasius] [1588-1653], who wrote 'De annis climactericis et de antiqua astrologia', published at Leyden in 1648. The Commentator of the 'Tractatus de judiciorum doctrina' in this MS., p. 85, line 9, states: 'Ego in libro meo de annis climactericis Saturnum hoc factum ostendi'.</bibl>
